plssem 0.1.0
  • Reference

oneIntOrdered

Source: R/datasets.R
oneIntOrdered.Rd

A simulated dataset.

Examples


m <- '
  X =~ x1 + x2 + x3
  Z =~ z1 + z2 + z3
  Y =~ y1 + y2 + y3

  Y ~ X + Z + X:Z
'

fit <- pls(m, oneIntOrdered)
summary(fit)
